    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it has been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained, so you can just hop in and go! It drives like a dream and still looks fantastic parked out front. I\u2019m looking for a smooth sale to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
