    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement and polyurethane bushings to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing service and valve adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain remains within factory tolerances. Equipped with a Bilstein monotube suspension setup, this example offers a precise, communicative steering rack and exceptional mechanical grip for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
